    schema:courseSchedule <https://guia-kg.skai.etsisi.upm.es/resource/93001312/2025-26/eventSchedule> ;
    schema:description "The foundations of optics and their application in the photovoltaic field are shown. In particular, the issue of concentration and its relation to angular acceptance and how both variables affect the cost of the concentration system are discussed. The student is also introduced to the engineering of optical devices other applications similar to the photovoltaic concentration such as those linked to the use of LEDs or wireless optical communications. The subject covers the theoretical foundations and methods of design and analysis up to the manufacturing and characterization techniques in optical engineering."@es ;
    schema:director <https://guia-kg.skai.etsisi.upm.es/resource/juancarlos.gonzalezl%40upm.es> ;
    schema:inLanguage "Inglés/Castellano"@es ;
    schema:instructor <https://guia-kg.skai.etsisi.upm.es/resource/juancarlos.gonzalezl%40upm.es> ;
    schema:name "Ingeniería óptica"@es .

